How to connect to the cluster

Locate the kubeconfig file called ukapizza.config

Setup context?

Create a configmap to see if the configuration works

kubectl create configmap getting-started --from-literal=uka=2019 -n<mynamespace>

Read the configmap back

kubectl get cm getting-started -oyaml -n<mynamespace>

Ensure that you are seeing the literal value that you specified when creating the configmap.
